tle\n!Released\n!Album\n|-\n|\"B.I.G.\" (D-Flow featuring Wande)\n|November 12, 2013<ref name=\":2\">{{Cite web|url=https://rapzilla.com/2013-11-d-flow-quarter-to-vinci/|title=D-Flow 'Quarter To Vinci'|last=Solis|first=Steven|date=2013-11-12|website=Rapzilla|language=en-US|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=2020-03-25}}</ref>\n|''Quarter to Vinci''\n|-\n|\"Gotta Go\" (Dru Bex featuring Jeremy Rodney-Hall and Wande)\n|April 13, 2018<ref>{{Citation|title=Gotta Go (feat. Jeremy Rodney-Hall & Wande) - Single by Dru Bex|url=https://music.apple.com/us/album/gotta-go-feat-jeremy-rodney-hall-wande-single/1364246340|language=en-us|access-date=2020-03-25}}</ref>\n|Non-album single\n|-\n|\"Level 3\" (Xay Hill featuring Silver Steph, Wande, Torey D'shaun, Roy Tosh, Raw B and Parris Chariz)\n|April 27, 2018<ref>{{Citation|title=Level 3 (feat. Silver Steph, Wande, Torey D'shaun, Roy Tosh, Raw B & Parris Chariz) - Single by Xay Hill|url=https://music.apple.com/us/album/level-3-feat-silver-steph-wande-torey-dshaun-roy-tosh/1375362050|language=en-us|access-date=2020-03-25}}</ref>\n|Non-album single\n|-\n|\"She Got Aesthetic\" (Not Klyde featuring Wande & Parris Chariz)\n|October 24, 2018<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EG5r6S19KmY|title=She Got Aesthetic (feat. Wande & Parris Chariz)|last=Not Klyde - Topic|first=|date=October 25, 2018|website=|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=March 25, 2020}}</ref>\n|''Lil Foil 39''\n|-\n|\"Groove\" (DJ Standout featuring Cass, Wande, and Eris Ford)\n|April 5, 2019<ref>{{Citation|title=Groove - Single by DJ Standout, Eris Ford, Wande & Cass|url=https://music.apple.com/us/album/groove-single/1456898210|language=en-us|access-date=2020-03-25}}</ref>\n|Non-album single\n|-\n|\"Holy Ghost\" (Mandela Dunamis featuring Wande)\n|May 31, 2019<ref>{{Citation|title=Holy Ghost (feat. Wande) - Single by Mandela Dunamis|url=https://music.apple.com/us/album/holy-ghost-feat-wande-single/1465973087|languag